## CLI Quick Start

### Build and Run

```bash
# Build
cargo build

# Run with Just
just run-cli --help

# Or run directly with cargo
cargo run --bin {{ package_name }} -- --help
```

### Basic Commands

```bash
# Say hello
just run-cli hello World

# With options
just run-cli hello "Rust Developer" --count 3 --uppercase

# Check version
just run-cli version

# Get JSON output
just run-cli version --json
```

### Example Session

```bash
$ just run-cli hello
Hello, World!

$ just run-cli hello "Rustacean" --count 2
[1/2] Hello, Rustacean!
[2/2] Hello, Rustacean!

$ just run-cli version
{{ package_name }} 0.1.0
Rust version: rustc 1.81.0
```
